Taylor Swift charts two albums in the top 10 on the Billboard 200 this week:

item.title:
‘Lover’ by Taylor Swift climbs to #6 on the Billboard 200 this week, with 38,000 units.
It debuted at #1 in 2019.
item.author: popcrave

item.title: ‘One Thing At A Time’ by Morgan Wallen becomes the longest-running #1 country album in over 30 years on the Billboard 200, surpassing Taylor Swift’s ‘Fearless’ (12 weeks).
item.author: popcrave

item.title: ‘One Thing At A Time’ by Morgan Wallen becomes the second album in history to spend its first 12 weeks at #1 on the Billboard 200, joining Stevie Wonder’s ‘Songs In The Key Of Life.’
item.author: popcrave
